{"tid":2007334,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有踢開波嘅你，有冇呢個腳患問題？","createTime":"2020-05-08T09:32:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T11:51:20.000Z","uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3daf395052a664e8531e9ed273a4d2696c4bc452","tid":2007334,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T09:32:32.000Z","msg":"我大大話話踢咗十幾年，自從知道自己個膝關節有啲問題就冇踢，宜家做lunges同glute bridge時，屈膝嗰一吓，個波羅蓋就會壓出痛楚，我懷疑入面嘅軟骨已經蝕得差唔多，點解懷疑關踢波事，係因為只有左膝痛，而左膝係以前射波隻腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以似係踢波嘅勞損，估計都係後生時代唔識強化個glute去穩定膝關節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9ec4fa798e81773e81c4e17a81c4c86e74ec938","tid":2007334,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T09:33:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CpD14TO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCpD14TO.png&h=cb95e842&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【郭偉强找數】<br />\n<br />\n呼籲集體投訴社工之恥郭偉强蓄意襲擊。<br />\n<br />\n郭偉强社工註冊編號：11071<br />\n罪行：普通襲擊<br />\n<br />\n下載「社會工作者註冊局」投訴表格<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.swrb.org.hk/Documents/complaint.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.swrb.org.hk%2FDocuments%2Fcomplaint.pdf&d=ZKl1Acg0IOD8KmAOqHMUQDMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=93cf67bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.swrb.org.hk/Documents/complaint.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"b2ab3d7455f0b9068398f0fbcf7b72418e3b43d6","tid":2007334,"uid":290421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3daf395052a664e8531e9ed273a4d2696c4bc452","tid":2007334,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T09:32:32.000Z","msg":"我大大話話踢咗十幾年，自從知道自己個膝關節有啲問題就冇踢，宜家做lunges同glute bridge時，屈膝嗰一吓，個波羅蓋就會壓出痛楚，我懷疑入面嘅軟骨已經蝕得差唔多，點解懷疑關踢波事，係因為只有左膝痛，而左膝係以前射波隻腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以似係踢波嘅勞損，估計都係後生時代唔識強化個glute去穩定膝關節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj